description: |
  This tower is at the northwestern point of the walls. From here
  you peer down into the deep gorge that separates the keep from
  the surrounding countryside. Gazing west, you see the cultivated
  fields and smoky hamlets of a properous kingdom. So different
  from the wild and dangerous woods east of the keep.
